	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam a domino, charissime mi Bullingere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Leonis in negocio <persName ref="person28">Buceri</persName> amicam dehortationem accepimus<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Der Brief, in dem <persName ref="person114">Leo Jud</persName> wie zuvor Bullinger (vgl. oben <ref target="file11007">Nr. 965</ref>, 2f) die <placeName ref="place121">Berner</placeName> vor einem Verbot von <persName ref="person28">Bucer</persName>-Schriften gewarnt haben muß, ist nicht erhalten.</note>, de qua non opus est multa tibi dicere.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non multis enim ante diebus mentem nostram accepisti<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Gemeint ist der Brief vom 8. März, oben <ref target="file11007">Nr. 965</ref>.</note>, licet tumultuarie opera amanuensis<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Der Brief ist von unbekannter Hand geschrieben.</note>, quando ob capitis fluxum ipse scribere non potui.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person114">Leo</persName> excusat <persName ref="person28">Bucerum</persName> non dolo, sed zelo omnia egisse.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nescio, an zelus dici queat ex ipsissima luce aliquem in abstrusissimas tenebras pertrahere velle, quod egit <persName ref="person28">Bucerus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si non satis esse videtur, expectemus, obsecro, paulisper, donec satis faciat, id quod haud dubie brevi futurum est.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">At sine vobis nihil tentabimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="98"/>Bene vale salvis omnibus fratribus, <persName ref="person14">Theodoro</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="person14">Theodor Bibliander</persName>.</note>, Bellicano<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="person165">Konrad Pellikan</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="person78">Beato</persName><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="person78">Beat Gering</persName>.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="place121">Bernę</placeName>, marcii 11. anno 37.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person145">Megander</persName> tuus totus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino Heinrico Bullingero, Tiguri Christum profitenti, fratri suo in domino charissmo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
